726131f-b.title: Queens: Bayside Avenue - 148th Street
726131f-b.text:
Bayside Ave., north side (looking east between 148th and 149th Streets), showing Henry W. Wickham home from 1860-1896. R. Hellman was the owner in 1926. Wickham's Estate comprised 47.6 acres. This is a set of two views, showing opposite side: of the house.
Anril 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
